    "body" : "<p><strong>Use regular expression:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>int i=Integer.parseInt(\"hello123\".replaceAll(\"[\\\\D]\",\"\"));\nint j=Integer.parseInt(\"123hello\".replaceAll(\"[\\\\D]\",\"\"));\nint k=Integer.parseInt(\"1h2el3lo\".replaceAll(\"[\\\\D]\",\"\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>output:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>i=123;\nj=123;\nk=123;\n</code></pre>\n"
