    "body" : "<p><strong>Use regular expression:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>String s=\"your1string2contain3with4number\";\nint i=Integer.parseInt(s.replaceAll(\"[\\\\D]\", \"\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>output:\ni=1234;</p>\n\n<p><strong>If you need first number combination then you should try below code:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>String s=\"abc123xyz456\";\nint i=NumberFormat.getInstance().parse(s).intValue();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>output:\ni=123;</p>\n"
