    "body" : "<p>You can also do it one line:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int hello = Integer.parseInt(((Button)findViewById(R.id.button1)).getText().toString().replaceAll(\"[\\\\D]\", \"\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Reading from order of execution </p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>grab the view using <code>findViewById(R.id.button1)</code></li>\n<li>use <code>((Button)______)</code> to cast the <code>View</code> as a <code>Button</code></li>\n<li>Call  <code>.GetText()</code>  to get the text entry from Button</li>\n<li>Call <code>.toString()</code> to convert the Character Varying to a String</li>\n<li>Call <code>.ReplaceAll()</code> with <code>\"[\\\\D]\"</code> to replace all Non Digit Characters with \"\" (nothing)</li>\n<li>Call <code>Integer.parseInt()</code> grab  and return an integer out of the Digit-only string.</li>\n</ol>\n"
