    "body" : "<h3>Kotlin</h3>\n<p>There are available Extension methods to parse them into other primitive types.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.text/kotlin.-string/to-int.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&quot;10&quot;.toInt()</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.text/kotlin.-string/to-long.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&quot;10&quot;.toLong()</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.text/kotlin.-string/to-boolean.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&quot;true&quot;.toBoolean()</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.text/kotlin.-string/to-float.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&quot;10.0&quot;.toFloat()</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.text/kotlin.-string/to-double.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&quot;10.0&quot;.toDouble()</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.text/kotlin.-string/to-byte.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&quot;10&quot;.toByte()</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.text/kotlin.-string/to-short.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&quot;10&quot;.toShort()</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Java</h3>\n<pre><code>String num = &quot;10&quot;;\nInteger.parseInt(num );\n</code></pre>\n"
